This is a 3D chess Board in FPS (1st Person Shooter Perspective) in Irrlicht, an open source 3D engine.
Irrlicht : irrlicht.sourceforge.net/
You start at position inside the board.
Use your down arrow key to move backwards out of the board.
Use the up arrow key to move forward; left and right to move left and right, respectively.
Use your mouse to look in a different direction.

